#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><pre>
#: en/devfs-guide.xml:247
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ <i>ls -l /dev/hda4</i>\n"
"lr-xr-xr-x    1 root     root           33 Aug 25 12:08 /dev/hda4 -> ide/host0/bus0/target0/lun0/part4\n"
